#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong>map view</strong>, your agents see where they need to head "
"for their interventions of the day. This visual aid will also help you plan "
"tasks so that each agent covers a specific area."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກ <strong>ມຸມມອງແຜນທີ່</strong>, ຕົວແທນຂອງທ່ານຈະເຫັນບ່ອນທີ່ພວກເຂົາຕ້ອງໄປເພື່ອດຳເນີນການໃນມື້"
"ນັ້ນ. ເຄື່ອງມືຊ່ວຍທາງສາຍຕານີ້ຍັງຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານວາງແຜນວຽກ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ຕົວແທນແຕ່ລະຄົນຮັບຜິດຊອບພື້ນທີ່ສະເພາະ."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Get an <strong>overview of the ratings</strong> you are receiving from the "
"'Field Service &amp;gt; Reporting &amp;gt; Customer Ratings' menu."
msgstr ""
"ເບິ່ງ <strong>ພາບລວມຂອງການໃຫ້ຄະແນນ</strong> ທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບຈາກເມນູ 'ການບໍລິການນອກສະຖານທີ່ > "
"ການລາຍງານ > ການໃຫ້ຄະແນນໂດຍລູກຄ້າ'."

#. module: certification_organism
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/certification_organism/static/src/js/my_tour.js:0
msgid "Get on track and explore our recommendations for your Odoo usage here!"
msgstr "ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ ແລະ ສຳຫຼວດຄຳແນະນຳຂອງພວກເຮົາສຳລັບການນຳໃຊ້ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານຢູ່ນີ້!"

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Get reporting on the various fields you are tracking during your "
"interventions. Identify recurring sources of issues and detect warning signs"
" of future potential issues."
msgstr ""
"ຮັບການລາຍງານກ່ຽວກັບຟິວຕ່າງໆ ທີ່ທ່ານກຳລັງຕິດຕາມໃນລະຫວ່າງການເຂົ້າດຳເນີນການ. ກວດສອບແຫຼ່ງທີ່ມາຂອງບັນ"
"ຫາທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊຳ້ ແລະ ກວດຫາສັນຍານເຕືອນຂອງບັນຫາທີ່ອາດຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນໃນອະນາຄົດ."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go back to the Quotation you had previously created, and hit that "
"'<strong>Confirm</strong>' button. Your Quotation is now a <strong>Sales "
"Order.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"ກັບໄປທີ່ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ສ້າງໄວ້ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້, ແລະ ກົດປຸ່ມ '<strong>ຢືນຢັນ</strong>'. ໃບສະເໜີລາຄ"
"າຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ກາຍເປັນ <strong>ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ແລ້ວ.</strong>"

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to 'Configuration &amp;gt; Worksheet Templates' and click on "
"'<strong>Analysis</strong>' from your '<strong>Worksheet Template</strong>' "
"form view."
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ 'ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ &amp;gt; ເທັມເພລດແຜ່ນວຽກ' ແລະ ຄລິກໃສ່ '<strong>ການວິເຄາະ</strong>' ຈາ"
"ກມຸມມອງແບບຟອມ '<strong>ເທັມເພລດແຜ່ນວຽກ</strong>' ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to 'Dashboards &amp;gt; Projects' to get an overview of your tasks. <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\">Use predefined </span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; background-color: inherit;\"><strong>dashboards</strong></span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\"> or build your own with the advanced reporting engine. Share filters with the team.</span>"
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ 'ແດຊບອດ > ໂຄງການ' ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງວຽກຂອງທ່ານ. <span style=\"color: "
"inherit; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\">ໃ"
"ຊ້ </span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; "
"background-color: inherit;\"><strong>ແດຊບອດ</strong></span>\n"
"                    <span style=\"color: inherit; font-style: normal; font-"
"weight: 400; background-color: inherit;\"> ທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ ຫຼື ສ້າງຂຶ້ນເອງດ້ວຍລະບົບການລ"
"າຍງານຂັ້ນສູງ. ແບ່ງປັນຟິວເຕີກັບທີມງານ.</span>"

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to Reporting &amp;gt; <strong>Tasks Analysis</strong> to get statistics "
"on your tasks and to analyze the performance of your projects."
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ ການລາຍງານ &amp;gt; <strong>ການວິເຄາະວຽກ</strong> ເພື່ອເບິ່ງສະຖິຕິກ່ຽວກັບວຽກຂອງທ່ານ "
"ແລະ ເພື່ອວິເຄາະປະສິດທິພາບຂອງໂຄງການ."

#. module: certification_organism
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:certification_organism.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Go to the 'Configuration &amp;gt; Stages' menu. Then define a '<strong>Rating Email Template</strong>' on your 'Done' stage (or any other one you'd like). This will automatically send a <strong>rating request</strong> to the\n"
"                    customer once the task reaches this stage."
msgstr ""
"ໄປທີ່ເມນູ 'ການຕັ້ງຄ່າ &amp;gt; ຂັ້ນຕອນ'. ຈາກນັ້ນກຳນົດ '<strong>ເທັມເພລດອີເມວການໃຫ້ຄະແນນ</"
"strong>' ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນ 'ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ' (ຫຼື ຂັ້ນຕອນອື່ນໆ ທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ). ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສົ່ງ <strong>ການຮ້ອງຂໍກ"
"ານໃຫ້ຄະແນນ</strong> ຫາລູກຄ້າໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ\n"
"                    ເມື່ອວຽກມາຮອດຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້."

